# Biometric Retention Policy

## 1. Purpose
This policy outlines the retention and destruction of biometric data.

## 2. Scope
Applies to all facial recognition and voiceprint data.

## 3. Retention Period
- **Active Users:** Retained for the duration of the account.
- **Inactive Users:** Deleted after 3 years of inactivity (BIPA compliance).

## 4. Destruction Method
- Secure overwrite (DoD 5220.22-M standard).
